article_title: Gaza death toll rises to 42,519, says Hamas-run health ministry.
sentence: In  its  latest  update,  Gaza's  Hamas-run  health  ministry  says  19  people  have  been  killed  and  91  others  wounded  in  the  past  24  hours.

article_title: Gaza death toll rises to 42,519, says Hamas-run health ministry.
sentence: At  least  42,519  Palestinians  have  been  killed  and  99,637  others  wounded  since  Israel  began  its  military  offensive  in  Gaza  after  the7  October  Hamas-led  attack,  the  health  ministry  adds.
